        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "Typically, assertion checking is enabled during program development and testing, and disabled for deployment, to improve performance."
            ]
          ]
        },
        "type": "quote",
        "version": 1,
        "inline_content": [
          {
            "Text": "Typically, assertion checking is enabled during program development and testing, and disabled for deployment, to improve performance."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "alive": true,
        "created_by": "bb760e2d-d679-4b64-b2a9-03005b21870a",
        "created_time": 1550518384125,
        "id": "49db2140-df83-4257-9587-2ab2bc543a0e",
        "ignore_block_count": true,
        "last_edited_by": "bb760e2d-d679-4b64-b2a9-03005b21870a",
        "last_edited_time": 1550518384125,
        "parent_id": "ccb1c8f9-dbf9-41e9-9847-18507c749cbd",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "Because assertions may be disabled, programs must not assume that the expressions contained in assertions will be evaluated. Thus, these boolean expressions should generally be free of side effects. Evaluating such a boolean expression should not affect any state that is visible after the evaluation is complete. It is not illegal for a boolean expression contained in an assertion to have a side effect, but it is generally inappropriate, as it could cause program behavior to vary depending on whether assertions were enabled or disabled."
            ]
          ]
        },
        "type": "text",
        "version": 1,
        "inline_content": [
          {
            "Text": "Because assertions may be disabled, programs must not assume that the expressions contained in assertions will be evaluated. Thus, these boolean expressions should generally be free of side effects. Evaluating such a boolean expression should not affect any state that is visible after the evaluation is complete. It is not illegal for a boolean expression contained in an assertion to have a side effect, but it is generally inappropriate, as it could cause program behavior to vary depending on whether assertions were enabled or disabled."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "alive": true,
        "created_by": "bb760e2d-d679-4b64-b2a9-03005b21870a",
        "created_time": 1550518384125,
        "id": "560c2fc1-e39d-4363-84af-53d0652afec1",
